sequenceDiagram
    participant CI as CI/CD Pipeline<br/>(GitHub Actions / Tekton)
    participant CLI as model-extractor CLI<br/>Go Binary
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant RHR as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem<br/>data/*.yaml
    participant Quay as Quay.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DC as Data Container<br/>odh-model-metadata-collection
    participant Dash as RHOAI Dashboard<br/>Consumer Pod

    Note over CI,Quay: Flow 1: Build-time Model Catalog Generation

    CI->>CLI: Execute model-extractor

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over CLI,HF: Step 1: Discover HuggingFace Collections
        CLI->>HF: GET /api/collections (Public API)<br/>No auth, 30s timeout
        HF-->>CLI: Model collections, READMEs,<br/>YAML frontmatter, tags
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over CLI,RHR: Step 2: Extract Model Cards from OCI Images
        CLI->>RHR: GET manifests + layer blobs<br/>Docker registry auth
        RHR-->>CLI: OCI manifests, model card layers<br/>(io.opendatahub.modelcar.layer.type annotation)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over CLI,FS: Step 3: Enrich, Process & Generate Catalogs
        CLI->>CLI: Parse model cards (YAML frontmatter + markdown)
        CLI->>CLI: Enrich metadata (family-aware matching)
        CLI->>CLI: Classify model types (generative/predictive)
        CLI->>CLI: Deduplicate and merge catalogs
        CLI->>FS: Write models-catalog.yaml
        CLI->>FS: Write validated-models-catalog.yaml
        CLI->>FS: Write other-models-catalog.yaml
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over CI,Quay: Step 4: Build & Push Data Container
        CI->>CI: docker build (ubi9-minimal base)
        CI->>Quay: Push container image<br/>Auth: QUAY_USERNAME/PASSWORD
        Quay-->>CI: Image pushed successfully
    end

    Note over DC,Dash: Flow 2: Runtime Data Consumption

    rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
        Dash->>DC: Volume mount /app/data
        DC-->>Dash: Catalog YAML files<br/>(read-only, non-root UID 1001)
    end
